                    <msContents>
                        <summary>Image of Mika'el and Gabri'el, The Anaphora of Our Lady Mary
                            attributed to Hareyakos of Behensa. Some fine illuminations. Small book,
                            with cloth covering and strip to cover foredges of the book. Mention is
                            made of owner, ኃይለ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡, and of scribe, in one place as ወልደ፡ አማኑኤል፡,
                            and in another as, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሀብተ፡
                            ማርያም፡</foreign></summary>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <textLang/>
                        </msItem>
                    </msContents>
